/> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a84f135a3efaa601a8dbc118526fb513e4558c","tid":470125,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/122221_1de042540ae9927b374091666f1145b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F122221_1de042540ae9927b374091666f1145b5.jpg&h=b00d2b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBackup 定先<br />\n明報反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb8ea6d795d3b6149ad1db4fa9f29507f542ab0","tid":470125,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/122221_1de042540ae9927b374091666f1145b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F122221_1de042540ae9927b374091666f1145b5.jpg&h=b00d2b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBackup 定先<br />\n明報反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a0fcc90afe7bf3a9cf3d2aeb7497b32487400f","tid":470125,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44f6b246325f73bf3a8eb10292e51a7da658386","tid":470125,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:28:26.000Z","msg":"堡主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd87fdb282c2f59c7b8b7afcc0792fea6ef842ae","tid":470125,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>堡主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李飛都係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f34043cf8a2b8352477deea5756879bdc6de2df","tid":470125,"uid":83344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"認識基本法就了解香港歷史？乜野邏輯"},{"pid":"e8949bf82481b9f1ad0d4b17cc8a1901e8001dfd","tid":470125,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"抵制反港獨, 即係支持港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac6ea671ed556ac75a9ab321e9b001536d77120","tid":470125,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"<strong> 李飛斥提倡港獨荒謬違法　應毫不猶豫抵制</strong><br />\n<br />\n昨晚(15日)抵港的全國人大常委會香港基本法委員會主任李飛，今早(16日)出席由港府在灣仔會展舉辦的研討會，主講「在國家憲法及《基本法》下香港作為特別行政區的角色和使命」。他批評，港獨不論打出何種旗號，均是荒謬違法，應毫不猶豫予以抵制。 <br />\n<br />\n李飛表示，今次的演講題目有三層意義，第一是「香港特區從何而來？」即是解答你從哪裡來的問題，第二是「香港特區在國家體制中有何種地位？」即是你是誰的問題，以及第三是「香港特區應該做什麼？」即是你要到哪裡去的問題。李飛稱只要解答好這三條問題，將可更好地認識自己，抓住定位，面向未來。 <br />\n<br />\n李飛特別提到中國憲法，他指中國憲法是香港特別行政區的根和源，所謂「參天之木，必有其根；懷山之水，必有其源」，稱若沒有中國憲法就沒有香港《基本法》，而沒有《基本法》就沒有香港特區、沒有一國兩制。李飛指出，近年有人稱《基本法》是香港憲法，卻忽略了國家憲法，甚至稱香港的憲制依據是《中英聯合聲明》，李飛強調這說法並不正確，因為中國是統一單一制國家，只能有一個憲法，便是中國憲法。 <br />\n<br />\n李飛重申，中國憲法是設立香港特區、實施一國兩制最根本、最權威的法律依據，而最近國家領導人和黨談到一國兩制的問題時，都會同時談到國家憲法和《基本法》，證明這種說法具有重大現實意義。 <br />\n<br />\n而談到港獨問題，李飛指近年來有些人抗拒「一國」、抗拒中央管治，提出本土自決、香港獨立，以各種歪理學說去否定、詆毀中央政府對香港的管治，否認香港是中國一部分的事實，甚至採用激進暴力方法，將分裂主義企圖訴諸行動。他批評，不論打出何種旗號，偽裝成甚麼口號理論，從行為上均是荒謬，亦是違法，在情感上亦不能容忍，應毫不猶豫予以抵制。 <br />\n<br />\n李稱，痛心有些青少年不明白國家及民族的歷史，不清楚香港的前世今生，被一些別有用心的人蠱惑荼毒，輕信了錯誤的觀念。他認為，為了保障香港的長期繁榮穩定，一國兩制長期實施，以及青年一代健康成長，必須樹立正確的國家觀念以及一國兩制。"},{"pid":"a739c8fa719111558170e8c548430bc14273d714","tid":470125,"uid":8129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"李飛真係幾勁 講野一針見血 句句刺中耶撚如何被洗腦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b635b6473fb383c7e3120b553e651bfe3a15f6e2","tid":470125,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47667f148154b381ea2eb91b1bb1052afbc0aa5a","tid":470125,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db9cd986fdb0c57a05e348f51fb00a7a6e463f5","tid":470125,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6d5609085c29bb11d89b62655296aa675f8e99","tid":470125,"uid":36964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你愈痛我愈開心呀仆街</span>"},{"pid":"ebe78e0fea4ed32e11bf948530ecd523dd82e592","tid":470125,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"你，非啦"}]}